{
  "texts": [
    "In 2023, a series of groundbreaking models have further propelled the field.",
    "BloombergGPT (Wu et al., 2023) emerged as a 50-billion parameter model trained on an extensive financial data corpus.",
    "Its training on a diverse dataset enabled it to excel in financial tasks while maintaining robust performance in general LLM benchmarks.",
    "PIXIU (Xie et al., 2023) followed, presenting a comprehensive framework with a financial LLM fine-tuned with instruction data.",
    "PIXIU was a crucial development in advancing the open-source development of financial AI, combining a novel instruction dataset and an evaluation benchmark for financial LLMs."
  ]
}